VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT @SelectProvider\s*\(|@UpdateProvider\s*\(|@InsertProvider\s*\(|@DeleteProvider\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:escapeSQL|sanitize|allowlist|validateColumn
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects MyBatis Provider annotations that dynamically build SQL queries.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for selectKey or Provider with Dynamic SQL Building.
